<p><strong>Important dates:</strong></p>

<p><strong>Full Papers, Short Papers, Posters &amp; Demonstrations:</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>3 April 2017 - Mandatory submission of an abstract</li>
  <li>10 April 2017 - Submission of full version</li>
  <li>29 May 2017 - Notification of acceptance</li>
  <li>26 June 2017 - Camera-ready versions</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Workshop Proposals:</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>10 April 2017 - Submission of workshop proposal (Abstract not needed)</li>
  <li>5 May 2017 - Workshop notification</li>
  <li>12 and 13 September 2017 - Workshops</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Project Meetings:</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>20 June 2017 - Room reservation for project meetings</li>
  <li>11, 12, 13 September 2017 - Project Meetings</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Conference:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>24 July 2017 - Early-bird registration ends</li>
  <li>14 and 15 September 2017 - Main conference</li>
</ul>

